net.bytebuddy.agent.builder

Interface AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer.CircularityLock

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer.CircularityLock.Active, AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer.CircularityLock.Inactive
    Enclosing class:
    AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer

    protected static interface AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer.CircularityLock
    A circularity lock is responsible for preventing that a ClassFileLocator is used recursively. This can happen when a class file transformation causes another class to be loaded.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes

      An active circularity lock.
      static class  AgentBuilder.Default.ExecutingTransformer.CircularityLock.Inactive
      An inactive circularity lock which is always acquirable.
